data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING A BUYER INCENTIVE OF $12,500.00 TO BE USED FOR BUYERS CLOSING COSTS AND/OR BUYER LENDER BUY-DOWN!  Nestled in East Texas, this meticulously maintained property presents a beautiful home on a 1.5-acre tree-lined lot with a saltwater swimming pool. The lower-level master suite opens to a patio overlooking the pool, offering relaxation. The central focus revolves around the formal dining, living room, and kitchen, seamlessly connecting indoor and outdoor spaces. On the upper floor, an expansive bonus room awaits, offering endless possibilities for customization. Whether envisioned as a cozy den, dynamic playroom, quiet library, efficient office, or engaging game room, this space caters to diverse needs and aspirations. For those seeking a peaceful, secluded, and visually enchanting residence in East Texas, this property stands as an exceptional contender. With a gas fireplace, walk-in closets, and elegant details throughout, this property is a serene haven that must be seen to fully appreciate its charm and appeal.
